            <abstract>
                <p>The text belongs to the Beta ʾƎsrāʾel (Ethiopian Jewish) literature. It is a renarration of the biblical story in
                    <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3194Susanna">Susanna</ref> , with Daniel replaced by Michael. It stands in close relation to the Christian 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3966Homily">Homily on the Archangel Michael (for Naḥase)</ref>.</p>
            </abstract>
